cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY 

This paper deals with the application of deep learning algorithms to solve problems related to ground robots and their interaction with terrain. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves image processing and classification, which suggests the category cs.CV (Computer Vision). The use of deep learning algorithms indicates the categories cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with the estimation of variables that affect the interaction between the robot and the terrain, which suggests the category cs.SY (Systems and Control).
